Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 12/25/2024

Ascend (“we,” “our,” or “us”) is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and disclose your personal information when you use the Ascend app and related services (collectively, the “Services”). By using our Services, you agree to the practices described in this policy.

1. Information We Collect

A. Information You Provide

Account Information: Name, email address, and password when you create an account.

Profile Information: Optional details such as preferences and study habits.

Payment Information: If you purchase a subscription, we collect billing details, but payment information is processed securely by third-party providers (e.g., Stripe, PayPal).

B. Information We Automatically Collect

Usage Data: Information about how you interact with the app, such as lessons completed, badges earned, and time spent on activities.

Device Information: Data about the device you use to access the Services, including device type, operating system, and IP address.

Cookies and Tracking Technologies: We use cookies to remember your preferences and enhance your experience.

C. Information from Third Parties

Third-Party Services: Information from services you connect to Ascend (e.g., social media login credentials).

2. How We Use Your Information

We use your information for the following purposes:

Provide and Improve Services: To personalize your experience, track progress, and deliver content tailored to your interests.

Billing and Payments: To process payments securely.

Communication: To send important updates, notifications, and promotional offers.

Analytics: To monitor usage patterns and improve the app’s functionality.

Compliance: To comply with legal obligations and protect against fraudulent or unauthorized activities.

3. How We Share Your Information

A. Service Providers

We share your information with trusted third-party service providers for purposes such as payment processing, data hosting, and analytics. These providers are bound by confidentiality agreements and cannot use your data for other purposes.

B. Legal Requirements

We may disclose your information to comply with applicable laws, regulations, or legal processes.

C. Business Transfers

If Ascend is involved in a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets, your information may be transferred as part of that transaction.

4. Your Rights and Choices

A. Managing Your Information

You can access, update, or delete your account information through the app’s settings.

B. Communication Preferences

You can opt out of promotional emails by following the unsubscribe link in the email. Note that you cannot opt out of essential service communications.

C. Data Deletion

If you wish to delete your account and associated data, please contact us at [support@ascendbible.com].

D. Cookie Management

You can manage cookie preferences through your browser settings.

5. Data Retention

We retain your information as long as necessary to provide the Services or comply with legal obligations. Once data is no longer needed, it is securely deleted.

6. Data Security

We implement robust security measures to protect your information. However, no system is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your data.

7. Children’s Privacy

Ascend is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under this age. If we become aware of such data, it will be promptly deleted.

8. International Users

If you access Ascend from outside the United States, you consent to the transfer and processing of your data in the United States, which may have different data protection laws.

9. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted within the app, and the “Effective Date” will be updated. Continued use of the Services indicates your acceptance of any changes.

10. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

Email: support@ascendbible.com

